text: Elin Borg (born 27 February 1990) is a Swedish football defender who currently plays for Södersnäckornas BK. She has played Damallsvenskan football for Linköpings FC, AIK, Kristianstads DFF. ==References== ==External links== * Category:Swedish women's footballers Category:Linköpings FC players Category:AIK Fotboll (women) players Category:Kristianstads DFF players Category:Djurgårdens IF Fotboll (women) players Category:Damallsvenskan players Category:1990 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football defenders
